e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被自殺"},{"pid":"24be6873ba0288f0964ce1aca8c40d6cf4d3b5c4","tid":1173291,"uid":130303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"count me in"},{"pid":"dcaa94948d24788ad11a778a3a33fab5cbff8a89","tid":1173291,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=d36d2b68\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad87ea28a9a1cabc56173e516334127d80d0479d","tid":1173291,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"香港咁細都有36人，真係好悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}